FBIS4-18773 "drweu069_j_94005" FBIS-WEU-94-069 Daily Report 9 Apr 1994 ITALY & VATICAN CITY Scalfaro Considers Tasking Berlusconi To Form Government Scalfaro Considers Tasking Berlusconi To Form Government LD0904114294 Rome RAI Televideo Teletext in Italian 1056 GMT 9 Apr 94 LD0904114294 Rome RAI Televideo Teletext Italian BFN [Excerpt] President "Scalfaro is thinking of giving Berlusconi the task of forming the new government, and this is what he told Bossi when he met him yesterday at the Presidency of the republic," Speroni, the head of the Northern League in the Senate, told a journalist of the Agenzia Italia. Speroni said that Berlusconi as prime minister would not be a problem "since he is not against federalism." [passage omitted]
